title: MPEDA Recruitment 2025 - Walk- in interview for 02 Lab Trainee Posts
description: The Marine Products Exports Development Authority (MPEDA) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 02 Lab Trainee Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed Any Degree and post-graduation can apply for the MPEDA Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview.
